data.text: Abiro tingʼo nyingi malo, yaye Nyasacha ma Ruoth;
Abiro paki pile ka pile
Jehova Nyasaye duongʼ miwuoro kendo owinjore gi pak,
Tiengʼ achiel biro pako tijeni ne tiengʼ machielo;
Gibiro wuoyo kuom duongʼni mangʼongo kendo marieny,
Gibiro nyiso kuom tekoni mitimogo gik malich miwuoro,
Gibiro loso nyasi mar ber ni mogundho
Jehova Nyasaye ngʼwon kendo kecho ji,
Jehova Nyasaye timo maber ne ji duto;
Ji duto ma isechweyo biro paki, yaye Jehova Nyasaye;
Gibiro nyiso ji kuom duongʼ mar pinyruodhi
mondo ji duto ongʼe gik madongo mitimo
Pinyruodhi en pinyruoth mochwere,
Jehova Nyasaye chungo ji duto mopodho
In ema wenge ji duto ngʼiyi,
Ka iyawo lweti
Jehova Nyasaye nikare e yorene duto
Jehova Nyasaye ni machiegni gi ji duto maluongo nyinge,
Ochopo dwaro mag joma omiye luor;
Jehova Nyasaye rito maber ji duto mohere,
Dhoga biro wacho pak ne Jehova Nyasaye.
